Text: Womens Initiative ReceptionHosted by VEs Paula Hinton Cc Good Morning We havent heard from you and the next event is around the corner Please see the information below and let us know if you will be joining us The Womens Initiative of United Way of the Texas Gulf Coast and Vinson Elkins LLP Cordially invite you to a networking reception for women supporting the United Way Tuesday February pm pm Hosted by Paula Hinton Place Inverness Houston Texas directions provided on the reverse side Please RSVP to Melissa Hulin at We look forward to seeing you there Melissa Hulin Fund Development Specialist United Way of the Texas Gulf Coast Direct Fax email
